So to recap with this approach:
  - if there is no flag, if "package.json" doesn't exist it will be created and later in the program updated;
  - if there is a flag and that package.json doesn't exist it will be created and later in the program updated;
 - if there is a flag and the package.json exists, it will not be recreated but will later in the program updated.

